## Configuration file for your app

## Declare the configuration parameters you want to use
Application.config do
  parameter :var1
  parameter :var2
  parameter :var3
end

## Change their values
Application.config do
  var1  "value"
  var2  ['one','two','three']
  var3  { :one=>1, :two=>2 }
end

